<Layout title="WordPress Development Sydney | Custom WordPress Sites | Cosmos Web Tech" description="Expert WordPress development in Sydney. Custom themes, WooCommerce stores, and plugin development for Hills District & Western Sydney businesses. From $2,000.">
  <!-- Header -->
