            <line x1="3" y1="18" x2="21" y2="18"/>
          </svg>
        </button>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Page Hero -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <nav class="breadcrumb">
        <a href="/">Home</a> / <a href="/services">Services</a> / <span>WordPress</span>
      </nav>
      <h1>WordPress Development Sydney</h1>
      <p>Custom WordPress websites you can easily manage yourself</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <section class="service-detail">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="service-grid">
        <div class="service-main">
          <h2>WordPress - The World's Most Popular CMS</h2>
          <p>WordPress powers over 40% of all websites on the internet, and for good reason. It's flexible, user-friendly, and can be customized to do almost anything. From simple blogs to complex e-commerce stores, WordPress is the go-to platform for businesses of all sizes.</p>

          <p>At Cosmos Web Tech, we specialize in custom WordPress development. We don't just install a theme and call it done - we build tailored solutions that match your brand and business needs perfectly.</p>

          <h3>Our WordPress Services</h3>

          <div class="features-grid">
            <div class="feature-item">
              <div class="feature-icon">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <path d="M12 19l7-7 3 3-7 7-3-3z"/>
                  <path d="M18 13l-1.5-7.5L2 2l3.5 14.5L13 18l5-5z"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h4>Custom Theme Development</h4>
              <p>Unique designs built from scratch to match your brand perfectly.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-item">
              <div class="feature-icon">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <circle cx="9" cy="21" r="1"/>
                  <circle cx="20" cy="21" r="1"/>
                  <path d="M1 1h4l2.68 13.39a2 2 0 0 0 2 1.61h9.72a2 2 0 0 0 2-1.61L23 6H6"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h4>WooCommerce Stores</h4>
              <p>Full e-commerce functionality with payment processing and inventory management.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-item">
              <div class="feature-icon">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"/>
                  <polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h4>Plugin Development</h4>
              <p>Custom plugins for functionality that off-the-shelf solutions can't provide.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-item">
              <div class="feature-icon">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <path d="M21 12.79A9 9 0 1 1 11.21 3 7 7 0 0 0 21 12.79z"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h4>Theme Customization</h4>
              <p>Modify existing themes to better suit your needs and branding.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-item">
              <div class="feature-icon">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h4>WordPress Migration</h4>
              <p>Move your existing site to WordPress or upgrade your current WordPress site.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-item">
              <div class="feature-icon">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h4>Security & Maintenance</h4>
              <p>Keep your WordPress site secure with updates, backups, and monitoring.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h3>Why Choose WordPress?</h3>
          <div class="why-wp">
            <div class="wp-reason">
              <h4>Easy to Manage</h4>
              <p>Update your content, add blog posts, and manage your site without any technical knowledge. The intuitive admin panel makes it simple.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="wp-reason">
              <h4>Cost Effective</h4>
              <p>WordPress is free and open source. You only pay for hosting, themes, and development - making it budget-friendly for small businesses.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="wp-reason">
              <h4>Infinitely Scalable</h4>
              <p>Start small and grow. WordPress can handle everything from a simple blog to a high-traffic enterprise website.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="wp-reason">
              <h4>SEO Friendly</h4>
              <p>WordPress is built with clean code that search engines love. Add SEO plugins and your site is optimized for Google.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h3>WordPress vs Custom Website</h3>
          <p>Not sure whether WordPress is right for you? Here's a quick comparison:</p>

          <table class="comparison-table">
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th>Feature</th>
                <th>WordPress</th>
                <th>Custom Build</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <td>Cost</td>
                <td>Lower upfront</td>
                <td>Higher upfront</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Timeline</td>
                <td>2-4 weeks</td>
                <td>4-8 weeks</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Ease of editing</td>
                <td>Very easy</td>
                <td>Depends on CMS</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Flexibility</td>
                <td>High (via plugins)</td>
                <td>Unlimited</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Best for</td>
                <td>Most businesses</td>
                <td>Complex applications</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <div class="service-sidebar">
          <div class="sidebar-card">
            <h3>WordPress Packages</h3>

            <div class="package">
              <h4>WordPress Starter</h4>
              <div class="package-price">From $2,000</div>
              <ul>
                <li>Premium theme setup</li>
                <li>Up to 10 pages</li>
                <li>Contact form</li>
                <li>SEO plugin setup</li>
                <li>Training session</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="package">
              <h4>WordPress Business</h4>
              <div class="package-price">From $4,000</div>
              <ul>
                <li>Custom theme design</li>
                <li>Unlimited pages</li>
                <li>Blog setup</li>
                <li>Advanced SEO</li>
                <li>Speed optimization</li>
                <li>3 months support</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="package">
              <h4>WooCommerce Store</h4>
              <div class="package-price">From $6,000</div>
              <ul>
                <li>Full e-commerce setup</li>
                <li>Payment gateway</li>
                <li>Up to 100 products</li>
                <li>Shipping integration</li>
                <li>Inventory management</li>
                <li>6 months support</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <a href="/contact?service=wordpress" class="btn btn-primary btn-large" style="width: 100%;">Get Quote</a>
          </div>

          <div class="sidebar-card">
            <h3>Maintenance Plans</h3>
            <p class="sidebar-text">Keep your WordPress site secure and running smoothly.</p>
            <div class="maintenance-options">
              <div class="maint-option">
                <strong>Basic</strong>
                <span>$50/mo</span>
              </div>
              <div class="maint-option">
                <strong>Standard</strong>
                <span>$100/mo</span>
              </div>
              <div class="maint-option">
                <strong>Premium</strong>
                <span>$200/mo</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <a href="/services/hosting" class="sidebar-link">Learn about maintenance →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta section-navy">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h2>Ready for a WordPress Site?</h2>
        <p>Get a free consultation and quote for your WordPress project.</p>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-white btn-large">Get Free Quote</a>
          <a href="tel:0433309677" class="btn btn-outline-white btn-large">Call 0433 309 677</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="footer-grid">
        <div class="footer-brand">
          <a href="/" class="logo footer-logo">
            <div class="logo-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 50 50" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <circle cx="25" cy="10" r="3" fill="#ffffff"/>
                <circle cx="10" cy="35" r="2.5" fill="#3b82f6"/>
                <circle cx="40" cy="35" r="2.5" fill="#3b82f6"/>
                <line x1="25" y1="13" x2="12" y2="33" stroke="#ffffff" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                <line x1="25" y1="13" x2="38" y2="33" stroke="#ffffff" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                <line x1="12" y1="35" x2="38" y2="35" stroke="#3b82f6" stroke-width="1.5"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="logo-text">
              <span class="brand-name" style="color: white;">Cosmos Web Tech</span>
              <span class="brand-tagline">Your Digital Universe</span>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="footer-links-col">
          <h4>Services</h4>
          <ul class="footer-links">
            <li><a href="/services/web-design">Web Design</a></li>
            <li><a href="/services/wordpress">WordPress</a></li>
            <li><a href="/services/ecommerce">E-commerce</a></li>
            <li><a href="/services/odoo">Odoo</a></li>
            <li><a href="/services/seo">SEO Services</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="footer-links-col">
          <h4>Company</h4>
          <ul class="footer-links">
            <li><a href="/about">About Us</a></li>
            <li><a href="/portfolio">Portfolio</a></li>
          <li><a href="/demos">Demos</a></li>
            <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="footer-links-col">
          <h4>Contact</h4>
          <ul class="footer-links">
            <li>Bella Vista, NSW 2153</li>
            <li><a href="tel:0433309677">0433 309 677</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="footer-bottom">
        <p>&copy; 2025 Cosmos Web Tech. ABN: 32 164 690 751. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy-dark) 0%, var(--navy) 100%);
    padding: 8rem 0 4rem;
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .breadcrumb {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .breadcrumb a { color: var(--grey-300); }
  .breadcrumb span { color: var(--grey-light); }

  .page-hero h1 {
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .page-hero p {
    color: var(--grey-300);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
  }

  .service-detail {
    padding: 5rem 0;
  }

  .service-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 380px;
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  .service-main h2 { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .service-main h3 {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .service-main p {
    color: var(--grey-dark);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .feature-item {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--grey-100);
    border-radius: 12px;
  }

  .feature-icon {
    width: 50px;
    height: 50px;
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: 10px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .feature-icon svg {
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    stroke: var(--accent);
  }

  .feature-item h4 {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .feature-item p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--grey);
  }

  .why-wp {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .wp-reason h4 {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .wp-reason p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .comparison-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .comparison-table th,
  .comparison-table td {
    padding: 1rem;
    text-align: left;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--grey-200);
  }

  .comparison-table th {
    background: var(--grey-100);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--navy-dark);
  }

  .sidebar-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--grey-200);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .sidebar-card h3 {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
  }

  .sidebar-text {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--grey);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .package {
    padding: 1.5rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--grey-200);
  }

  .package:last-of-type {
    border-bottom: none;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .package h4 { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }

  .package-price {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .package ul { list-style: none; }

  .package li {
    padding: 0.25rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    position: relative;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--grey-dark);
  }

  .package li::before {
    content: '✓';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--success);
  }

  .maintenance-options {
    margin: 1rem 0;
  }

  .maint-option {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 0.75rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--grey-200);
  }

  .maint-option:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .sidebar-link {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .cta {
    padding: 5rem 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta h2 {
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cta p {
    color: var(--grey-300);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .btn-outline-white {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--white);
    border: 2px solid var(--white);
  }

  .btn-outline-white:hover {
    background: var(--white);
    color: var(--navy-dark);
  }

  .nav-links a.active {
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .service-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .features-grid,
    .why-wp {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .comparison-table {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
    }

    .cta-buttons {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }
  }
</style>
